~] minute rest 
~2 minutes rest 
~2 minutes rest 
~2 minutes rest 
~] minute rest 
~ 2 minutes rest 
~2 minutes rest 
~] minute rest 
| 
~2 minutes rest 
~2 minutes rest 
~] minute rest 
~2 minutes rest 
~2 minutes rest 
